entries.title_d: Travel to the Corellia system and jam the Rebel communications relay point. When you enter the Corellia system you will receive a navigation waypoint to the Rebel communications relay point. Travel to this waypoint and wait for the jamming operation to begin. In order to succeed, you need to stay near the navigation waypoint. If you move to far away you will receive a warning message for you to return. Once the jamming operation begins the Rebels will send out fighters to attack you. Defend yourself against attack but do not leave the area until the jamming operation is completed.
entries.title: Corellia System: Jam the Rebel Communications
entries.quest_reachpoint_d: Once you have arrived at the navigation waypoint, wait until the jamming operation begins. Once the operation begins, you will need to remain in the area until it completes. You will receive regular updates on how long you have until the operation is over. If you move to far away from the navigation waypoint you will receive a warning message. If you remain outside of the area for to long the mission will fail.
entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the Corellia system and jam the Rebel communications relay point. Once in the Corellia system you will receive a navigation waypoint to the Rebel communications relay point. Travel to that location and wait for the jamming operation to begin.
entries.quest_defendpoint_t: Defend the Rebel Communications Relay Point
entries.quest_defendpoint_d: When you begin jamming the Rebel communications, they will send out fighters to try to destroy you. Defend yourself but do not leave the area until the operation is completed.

entries.mission_complete: The mission is a success, return to base.
entries.found_loc: Excellent, the counter attack has been scrambled.  Go to this position, it will cause the attack craft to make multiple jumps and stagger the assault.
